OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News London TfL
OL,8,FEnforcement Officer Harry Betts said:
OL,9,F"Day-to-day on the lower end there's
OL,10,Fjust casual verbal aggression and
OL,11,Fpeople swearing as they pass through
OL,12,Fthe gates.
OL,14,F"On the higher end you have people
OL,15,Fthreatening members of staff and
OL,16,Fpeople pushing members of staff out of
OL,17,Fthe way to get through the gates.
