OL,7,F"It's quite horrible, especially when
OL,8,Fyou're trying to do your job. We're
OL,9,Fhere to maintain the safety of our
OL,10,Fstaff and other people."
OL,12,FTfL says it takes violence and
OL,13,Faggression against staff "really
OL,14,Fseriously". Chief Operating Officer
OL,15,FClaire Mann added:
OL,17,F"We are launching a hard hitting anti-
OL,18,Fworkplace violence campaign which is
OL,19,Ffocusing on examples of people who've
OL,20,Fbeen brought to justice as a result of
OL,21,Fabusing our staff.
